{"tid":2385393,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是靚午 意大利西西里青醬焗雞上腿 配 青醬沙律汁 拼 燒粟米著仔沙律","createTime":"2021-01-29T04:12:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-29T09:01:53.000Z","uid":33359,"like":30,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"d8c89eba76818baba1748dbe8335eb502a2dd7b9","tid":2385393,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T04:12:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RH4fhSQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRH4fhSQ.jpg&h=cb786241&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nDRtCS4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnDRtCS4.jpg&h=cea2ec39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n講吓味道先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雞扒皮燒到好脆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n肉都仲係好嫩滑<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n青醬我覺得香草味唔夠重<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n整得青醬不妨重手少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我剩係食到好微弱既芫茜味<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但都係好食既<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n著仔沙律今日個味重返啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食落幾c伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5328ca0ff8fb670bf843e88d2e3eeafcaf0bba3e","tid":2385393,"uid":184233,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T04:13:12.000Z","msg":"是靚午師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"863f7d370baa4405131de867f449911b80e6bc49","tid":2385393,"uid":114873,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T04:13:16.000Z","msg":"邊度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eb0db9408eec11aaf72da70bd7cd8e67bc81e21","tid":2385393,"uid":369075,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29